title: Tin Foil Hat # 66: (We go to the vault for Presidents' Day)Special Swapcast with Grimerica
description: Happy President's Day from the Tin Foil Hat podcast!  The studio is closed today so we've decided to drop a special patreon episode that we recorded last November with the guys from the Grimerica podcast.  Enjoy your national holiday celebrating a President you all hate.  We will be back in the studio this Thursday with Jim Florentine!
itunes:author: Sam Tripoli
